      "span_text": "The collapse of Corti's organ continued in the basal turn of the untreated side leaving a flat epilthelium that has previously been described in severe aminoglycoside injury in guinea pigs. As noted in the aforementioned study, the overly damaged epithelium does not appear to respond to Atoh1, possibly explaining some of the limits of hair cell recovery that are seen in this series of experiments."
